hackathon-description-text: sudo HackStetson is a 24-hour hackathon held at Stetson University in DeLand, FL. We are inviting 200 hackers all over the nation to join us down here in the sunshine state for a weekend of fun, innovation, and networking. We are even offering travel reimbursement for this event on a first-come-first-serve basis.
